parameters:
There are Imperial soldiers in just the right
place!
Excuse me, gentlemen, may I have a word?

I have some questions for you. If you cooperate, I
won't take your life.

Hmm, who are you? Could it be, you're a comrade of
the Resistance?

This guy... a modified soldier...? Hehe! Finally,
someone who looks a bit strong has arrived!

Understood! I'll beat this guy up and return
immediately!
What's this, you're all talk and no action.

(Ah...what...my body's movements are sluggish...is
something malfunctioning...?)
Shuu! Shuu, can you hear me...⁉
Even the communication function is no good...⁉
Hey, hey! Don't just stand there spacing out!

Hmm...! I thought this one was unusually sturdy,
turns out it's a cyborg!

Interesting! Let's compare which is superior, this
body bestowed upon me by President Waltin or your
piece of junk.

Hahahahaha! You have quite a sturdy body, but I
wonder how long it will last!
Good! Captain! Keep beating her down like that!

Hehehe...! That's fine too, but since we're here!
Let's see what's inside this one.
Uhyahya! It's a cyborg disassembly show!
I'm going to punch you directly in the guts!

Hyahaha! Amazing, she's still alive! As expected
of a cyborg.

Uhyahya! What's this, what's this! Does the
Resistance's cyborg come with a womb~?

Stop it! Stop it! Let go of me with those filthy
hands!

Gyahahaha! Is the Resistance planning to start
breeding cyborgs!?

I'll kill all of you! Absolutely! I'll definitely
kill you!
If you can do it, then try!
Alright you guys, do as you please from here on!

Hehehe! We've been thoroughly troubled by the
Resistance! It's time to give them a hearty thank
you!

That's right! Let's make her an auction item too,
you guys just make sure not to kill her.

Hehehe! We're lucky our captain is kind, but I
wonder if we can sell her if she becomes such a
scrap?

That might be true, hey, make sure she doesn't
remain unsold! Gyahahaha!
(Shuu... please... come to save me... Shuu...)
